      "source_stream": "procedural",
      "statement": "theorem procedural_RingAut_coe_pow_0f1107dd7159 : (\u2200 {R : Type _} [Ring R] {a b : R} [Invertible a] [Invertible b] [Invertible (a + b)] (h : \u215f(a + b) = \u215fa + \u215fb),\n    a * \u215fb * a = b * \u215fa * b) \u2192\n  ((\u2200 {R : Type _} [Mul R] [Add R] (f : R \u2243+* R) (n : \u2115), \u21d1(f ^ n) = (\u21d1f)^[n]) \u2227\n    (\u2200 {R : Type _} {S : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring R] [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring S] (f : R \u2192+ S),\n      (\u2200 (x y : R), f (x * y) = f x * f y) \u2194 AddMonoidHom.mul.compr\u2082 f = (AddMonoidHom.mul.comp f).compl\u2082 f)) := by\n  sorry",
